'''Dr. Keating''' is the OB/GYN whom [[Meredith Grey]] saw after her miscarriage.

==History==
After her miscarriage, Meredith went to Dr. Keating and had tests run to find out if anything would prevent her from getting pregnant again. The tests showed that Meredith had a hostile uterus, which caused her miscarriage and would make it difficult for her to maintain another pregnancy.

==Career==
Dr. Keating is an attending OB/GYN.
